postcontent: The NRA Defensive Pistol Course is designed to develop the knowledge, skills and attitude to responsibly carry and use a concealed pistol safely, ethically and with confidence for personal protection. This 4 hour course focuses on technique and the development of a defensive mindset. A NRA certified instructor authorized to teach this course will interview each prospective student to determine if he/she has sufficient background and skills to take this course. Range time includes presenting from a quality strong side hip holster, performing speed reloads and immediate action drills, clearing malfunctions, and engaging targets. Students will need the following: A suitable defensive pistol Strong side outside the waistband belt holster for the pistol that will be used A belt able to support the pistol Additional magazines (at least four are recommended) Belt mounted magazine holder if available 200 rounds of factory new ammunition Eye and ear protection This is a fast paced shooting course with many drills. The instructors will emphasize movement and the use of cover. The FBI Qualification target will be used and a passing score must be achieved. title: For Sale:  1967 remington 700 varmit special
postcontent: Remington 700 varmit special in 6mm remington.  PAY ATTENTION!  Remington came out with the remington 700 in 1962.  The magnum calibers had stainless steel barrels.  In 1967 Remington came out with its first varmit special { heavy barrel).  The first few varmit barreled rifles had stainless steel barrels ( designated by a SS preceding the barrel code).  The barrel code on this rifle is AP, making the production date as March 1967.  The latter part of 1967 Remington stopped using stainless steel barrels to reduce costs. The barrel code on this rifle is SS AP 64.  The 1967 and early 1968 rifles had the stocks with the Fluer markings in the checkering.  I have shot this rifle to make sure it functions.  Wood and metal are excellent.  Has the factory aluminum butt plate.  Call for picstures and any further history or questions.  THIS INFO PROVIDED BY REMINGTON AT REDACTED opt.7.  My name is Steve REDACTED.  Serial number is 234472.  Make me an offer
